  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Flow 1 \u2014 Starting & Signaling Workflows",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "\nCustomer API calls that **create or modify** workflow state. The hot path: a caller is blocked\nwaiting for the response, so these surface in alerts fast. **SLO p99 < 200ms** (yellow), 1s (red).\n\nTranslated from `the signal flow`. Per-namespace and internal storage panels dropped\n(see Overview). Errors shown by operation (OSS `service_errors` has no `error_type` label).\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Frontend",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Start / Signal RPS by Operation",
      "description": "",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_requests{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution\"}[$rate]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Start / Signal Errors by Operation",
      "description": "",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 4,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(service_errors{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution\"}[$rate]) OR on() vector(0))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Start / Signal Latency p99 by Operation",
      "description": "",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15
      },
      "id": 5,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.2
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (operation, le) (rate(service_latency_bucket{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|SignalWithStartWorkflowExecution\"}[$rate])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
